          "slidetitle": "Introducing AI in Welfare Systems",
          "subtitle": "How AI shapes welfare eligibility today",
          "slidecontent": "• AI tools now help governments decide who qualifies for benefits and financial support\n• These systems analyse applications, flag anomalies, and rank claimants automatically\n• Faster processing\n• Decisions that once took weeks can now happen in minutes\n• Errors or biases in the data can lead to unfair outcomes for vulnerable people\n• Millions of people affected globally"
        },
